# Branch Workflow

- Treat `main` as the stable integration branch.
- Never make code changes directly on `main`.
- Before any code edit, create or switch to a feature/fix branch from `main`.
- Use branch names like `feature/...`, `fix/...`, or `chore/...`.
- Open pull requests into `main` for all changes.
- Merge via PR after checks pass; do not bypass PR flow.
- Do not recreate or use `develop` as a working branch.
